NODEJS et NVM:
- sudo snap install node --classic
then install nvm: https://github.com/nvm-sh/nvm#installing-and-updating
- curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.5/install.sh | bash
finally, change the version of node via nvm: https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-node-js-on-ubuntu-20-04-fr
or https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/how-to-update-node-and-npm-to-the-latest-version/
